item.title: Thanks liz...
item.description: So my friend liz sent me a belated birthday gift. It was some of her mens geek jewlery from her pretty successful zellestyle line of stuff. Neat stuff. She sent me a midi bracelet and some little nice black wire bracelets. I am happy because i had just thought about wearing bracelets again and i was tired of my custom devil gauntlets that i used to wear. Thanks liz. You should check out Liz’s stuff.
